  "html": "<p><strong>Status:</strong> Historical protocol work. Nostr is not a live feature of the current Desktop MVP or an active roadmap commitment.</p>\n<p>Nostr appeared repeatedly as a neutral protocol layer rather than a single product feature. OpenAgents explored it for identity, plugin discovery, key-value storage, data vending, client communication, job requests, and market coordination.</p>\n<h2 id=\"ideas-worth-retaining\"><a class=\"docs-heading-anchor\" href=\"#ideas-worth-retaining\">Ideas worth retaining</a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>User-controlled identity and signing should remain distinct from application accounts.</li>\n<li>Relay discovery is not the same as service availability or trust.</li>\n<li>Events need typed schemas, bounded permissions, provenance, and replay rules before they can carry product authority.</li>\n<li>Open protocols can reduce platform capture, but they do not remove custody, moderation, spam, privacy, or verification problems.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The workspace retains shared Nostr engineering in <code>nostr-effect</code> for protocol-level reuse. That repository presence is substrate, not evidence that OpenAgents Desktop exposes Nostr identity, relays, messaging, jobs, or markets.</p>\n<h2 id=\"historical-source-trail\"><a class=\"docs-heading-anchor\" href=\"#historical-source-trail\">Historical source trail</a></h2>\n<p>The build-in-public series explored a <a href=\"https://github.com/OpenAgentsInc/openagents/blob/main/docs/transcripts/066.md\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Nostr plugin registry</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/OpenAgentsInc/openagents/blob/main/docs/transcripts/082.md\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Nostr login</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/OpenAgentsInc/openagents/blob/main/docs/transcripts/088.md\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Nostr key-value storage</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/OpenAgentsInc/openagents/blob/main/docs/transcripts/142.md\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">data vending machines</a>, and a <a href=\"https://github.com/OpenAgentsInc/openagents/blob/main/docs/transcripts/177.md\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Nostr client</a>. Those episodes are historical orientation, not current product documentation.</p>\n",
